      "ruleId": "ias12-r002",
      "paragraphReference": "IAS 12.24",
      "ruleText": "An entity shall recognise a deferred tax liability for all taxable temporary differences, except for the initial recognition exemption for certain assets and liabilities in a transaction that is not a business combination.",
