      "ruleId": "ias12-r003",
      "paragraphReference": "IAS 12.34",
      "ruleText": "An entity shall recognise a deferred tax asset for deductible temporary differences, unused tax losses and unused tax credits to the extent that it is probable that taxable profit will be available.",
